    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/eaba004d068975a7f364e7b57a22cb9b.poster.avif?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/eaba004d068975a7f364e7b57a22cb9b.webm?t=1588300610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/eaba004d068975a7f364e7b57a22cb9b.mp4?t=1588300610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《魔弹术师》是一款动作竞技游戏，玩家使用“魔弹”相互对抗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/8e535be36a669fd26a2fd7f648262521.poster.avif?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/8e535be36a669fd26a2fd7f648262521.webm?t=1588300610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/8e535be36a669fd26a2fd7f648262521.mp4?t=1588300610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“弹幕开发”功能助你亲自打造对敌利器，弹道、弹速、子弹大小及色彩均可深度定制，通过这些元素的排列组合，玩家能够创造的弹幕堪称无穷无尽！尽情挥洒创意、制定战术，让你的敌人措手不及，将胜利收入囊中。玩家还可使用Steam创意工坊，将自己设计的弹幕与全世界分享。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/3c52eddde719a64a929fdc2e48cc3f5c.avif?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br>在单人游玩的“剧情模式”中，玩家将以制霸年度大赛、成为最强魔法骑士为目标，作为一名初出茅庐的术师参加魔弹术师联赛。在逐渐攻破剧情模式的过程中，玩家将逐渐解锁新的弹幕。它们既可以直接投入战斗，也能作为原创弹幕的模板。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137110/extras/557d6c05a61a6bdb950364822a32d7cc.avif?t=1588300610\" width=616 height=172 /></span><br>对战模式支持本地与在线多人对战，玩家可以与朋友切磋娱乐，也可以与全世界的对手随机匹配，一决高下。",
